</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-dtMgUX gYEGeC pf-69_ pf-heading-1-h3"><strong>Health and safety regulations
</strong></h3><p class="sc-cZMNgc hqfPHB pf-71_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Ensuring the safety of visitors and staff is paramount. The RA complies with the Health and Safety at Work etc. Act 1974, conducting regular risk assessments and implementing stringent health and safety protocols.





























